room_title: Escape room "Blackbeard’s Revenge" by Crack the Code in Laconia
room_description: Your captain is the infamous Blackbeard himself, and this is no life for you. Blackbeard has gone ashore for some rum and some trouble. This is your chance. Break into his quarters to find his secret treasure map and make your escape. But he’ll be back soon, and if he catches you, all you’ll find is Blackbeard’s Revenge!
